Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.47,0:00:05.07,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}As times change,\Ndifficult cases increase in number!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.07,0:00:07.31,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Today is alibi destruction.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.31,0:00:09.54,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Use someone and you'll pay!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.54,0:00:11.35,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}He sees the single truth for what it is,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.35,0:00:13.55,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}and looks like a kid but has the mind of an adult.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.55,0:00:15.52,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}His name? Detective Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.80,0:01:42.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Dr. Agasa...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.31,0:01:48.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When are we going to find any clues\Nabout those men in black?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.06,0:01:50.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You said that if I made old man Mouri famous
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.99,0:01:55.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,he'd get more clients and then maybe we'd find out about them...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.53,0:01:57.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He got more clients, didn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.60,0:02:02.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, but we haven't heard anything about those guys...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.60,0:02:04.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just be patient.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.87,0:02:09.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Act hastily and they might find out about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.88,0:02:11.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If that happens—
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.69,0:02:13.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.08,0:02:16.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It might put Ran and the old man in danger!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.95,0:02:19.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait quietly for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.09,0:02:22.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A detective needs patience too, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.76,0:02:27.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Say, what kind of experiment is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.50,0:02:30.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, this? It's a—
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.07,0:02:40.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now do you know what kind?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.31,0:02:44.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah. A dangerous one.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.45,0:02:53.25,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}What a lousy situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.25,0:02:54.86,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.86,0:02:57.65,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}It's old man Mouri. What's he doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.46,0:03:06.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Excellent choice, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.93,0:03:10.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could I have your address, sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.81,0:03:14.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.84,0:03:16.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What are you up to?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.42,0:03:19.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shh! I'm working!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.88,0:03:23.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, are you following that guy around?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.42,0:03:26.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, now! What if he notices me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.42,0:03:28.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Get outta here, kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.09,0:03:31.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Go tell Ran I won't be home for dinner!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.70,0:03:39.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't mind me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.73,0:03:42.07,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Gimme a break.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.51,0:03:52.98,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Gunma Prefecture Akaoni Village Fire Festival\NSunday, November 10th
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.12,0:04:34.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Talk about an easy job!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.05,0:04:37.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Half a million yen just for watching someone for three days!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.42,0:04:40.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Some jobs really rake in the dough!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.19,0:04:44.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's because everyone admires your great detective work!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.90,0:04:52.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even I'm amazed at how I've solved one case after another!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.37,0:04:55.08,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I solved them all.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.08,0:04:57.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come to think of it, your job's been going well
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.44,0:05:00.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,ever since Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} came!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.71,0:05:05.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe he brought some good luck with him!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.25,0:05:06.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's silly...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.79,0:05:10.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ran. How long are we gonna take care of this twerp?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.86,0:05:14.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are his parents still in the hospital?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.26,0:05:19.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Actually, when I visited Dr. Agasa yesterday...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.47,0:05:22.07,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}They did get out of the hospital,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.07,0:05:25.17,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}but then they suddenly got transferred overseas...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.17,0:05:27.61,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}They left yesterday!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.61,0:05:29.98,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Eh? They just left Conan{\rHonorifics - Thoughts\be10}-kun{\r\be10} behind?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.98,0:05:35.45,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}They said they'll send for him once they settle in.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.45,0:05:38.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So we're taking care of him again?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.62,0:05:40.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What was I supposed to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.55,0:05:42.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He has nowhere else to go...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.69,0:05:45.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So basically, you've been abandoned.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.60,0:05:47.39,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.39,0:05:51.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If I ever talk to his parents, I'll have to charge them for his upbringing...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.73,0:05:53.43,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Hey, now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.43,0:05:56.90,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}At 8:00 PM today, a man's body was found
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.90,0:06:02.04,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}under the burning tower of the Akaoni Fire Festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.04,0:06:04.31,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}According to his personal effects,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.31,0:06:07.35,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}the body was that of\N42-year-old Masaki Negishi{\rHonorifics - Radio\be10}-san{\r\be10}.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.35,0:06:08.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.75,0:06:11.05,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}—are investigating this as a possible murder—
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.05,0:06:14.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is the guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.82,0:06:17.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What is it, Dad? Did you know him?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.49,0:06:19.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Not just that...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.43,0:06:23.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was with him for three whole days!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.50,0:06:24.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Three days?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.38,0:06:25.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You can't mean—
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.80,0:06:30.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right. He's the guy I followed around until yesterday...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.20,0:06:33.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,...Masaki Negishi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.15,0:06:43.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dad sure is taking a long time\Nto give his statement.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.22,0:06:44.62,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}It's to be expected—
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.62,0:06:48.79,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}he was with the guy up until yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.79,0:06:52.63,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}The police don't get many witnesses like him!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.63,0:06:54.86,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}What kind of case is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.86,0:06:59.93,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Come on, old man! I can't wait to find out!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.07,0:07:04.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right. Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.26,0:07:06.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Half a billion yen?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.24,0:07:10.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes. The late Negishi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} had a life insurance policy
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.08,0:07:11.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,worth half a billion yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.98,0:07:13.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Doesn't it seem strange?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.71,0:07:16.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why would he give all that insurance money
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.72,0:07:22.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,to an ordinary friend like you, Yutaka Abe{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.09,0:07:27.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And you're the one who hired me to trail him!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.26,0:07:31.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why would he give you the insurance money?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.00,0:07:32.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was a game.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.65,0:07:34.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.37,0:07:38.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We had been friends since college.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.54,0:07:42.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When we went drinking one day, he—
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.08,0:07:45.68,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}We're not young anymore...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.68,0:07:50.02,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Wanna bet on who lives the longest?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.02,0:07:52.55,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Sounds interesting!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.55,0:07:57.29,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}How does half a billion yen sound?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.29,0:08:00.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,...and I accepted his invitation.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.16,0:08:03.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So you both took out 500-million yen policies.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.56,0:08:08.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I had no idea the bet would last only three months...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.14,0:08:11.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then why did you have Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} trail him?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.24,0:08:14.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No big reason, really.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.68,0:08:17.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He recently told me
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.34,0:08:21.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,that he thought someone was out to kill him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.52,0:08:23.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Out to kill him?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.58,0:08:26.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I thought he was joking at first,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.39,0:08:28.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but he wasn't acting quite normal,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.86,0:08:33.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,so I had Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} watch him for a few days.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.09,0:08:36.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.76,0:08:40.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, I have work to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.17,0:08:43.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I run a small business, so I'm actually quite busy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.07,0:08:51.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please find Negishi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s killer as quickly as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.41,0:08:55.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll contact you the instant we do!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.98,0:08:59.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I look forward to it, Detective.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.56,0:09:07.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's the only one I can see as the killer,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.36,0:09:09.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but he has an alibi.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.63,0:09:14.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,An airtight one, at that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.13,0:09:19.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Something's fishy! He's definitely the killer!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.31,0:09:20.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Half a million yen!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.67,0:09:23.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just to follow a guy for three days!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.58,0:09:25.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's way too much!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.38,0:09:28.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And his confident attitude!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.15,0:09:30.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm not too fond of that, either!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.75,0:09:33.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then why can't they arrest him?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.25,0:09:35.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,His alibi is perfect!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.52,0:09:41.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And I was the one who verified it for him!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.20,0:09:48.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The body was found on Sunday night,\Nduring the Fire Festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.54,0:09:51.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was on his tail the entire time
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.87,0:09:55.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,until the night before.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.21,0:09:58.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In other words, the crime took place
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.55,0:10:02.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,between late Saturday night and Sunday evening,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.05,0:10:04.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,when the flame tower was lit.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.05,0:10:08.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then the person you suspect must've done it during then...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.99,0:10:10.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.79,0:10:16.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He was on a company trip to Kyushu
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.90,0:10:20.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,from Saturday morning until this afternoon!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.57,0:10:23.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then why are you so fixated on him?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.70,0:10:28.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My detective's intuition...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.48,0:10:30.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.34,0:10:32.11,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}His alibi, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.51,0:10:39.01,Character Card,,0,0,0,,One Week Later
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.32,0:10:40.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.71,0:10:42.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.86,0:10:46.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That damn Abe got Negishi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s insurance money!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.99,0:10:50.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He got the half-billion yen just like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.43,0:10:53.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm going to destroy his alibi, no matter what!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.20,0:10:56.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What are those?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.94,0:11:00.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The schedule and pictures of his Kyushu trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.71,0:11:04.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I asked Inspector Megure to let me borrow them.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.28,0:11:07.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There has to be a clue in one of these photos.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.48,0:11:11.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just you watch! I, the great Kogoro Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sama{\r},
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.22,0:11:14.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,will expose his trick!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.19,0:11:17.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dad's on fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.36,0:11:19.56,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Let's just hope he doesn't burn out.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.56,0:11:25.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But Dad, couldn't he have come back on short notice on a domestic flight?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.03,0:11:29.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, it's very possible. But his alibi has no holes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.90,0:11:36.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Especially during the time the murder occurred.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.14,0:11:39.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He played mahjong with his employees all Saturday night.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.08,0:11:41.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sunday afternoon, he toured the city on bus.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.92,0:11:44.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He has pictures to prove it, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.39,0:11:46.55,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}These photos!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.49,0:11:53.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The only time he was alone was when he took a 2-hour nap Sunday afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.26,0:11:58.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It would be impossible to go to Gunma and back in that amount of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.93,0:12:02.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's so funny?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.40,0:12:04.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,These photos are weird!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.63,0:12:05.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Weird?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.44,0:12:07.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,See, look!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.71,0:12:10.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's by a clock in every one!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.71,0:12:12.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now that you mention it...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.95,0:12:15.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He must really like clocks!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.75,0:12:17.22,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}That's not normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.22,0:12:21.46,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}It's almost like he took these to prove his alibi.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.46,0:12:23.86,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}And the kid's right—
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.86,0:12:25.76,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Wait a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.76,0:12:29.63,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}It seems like whenever I'm stuck on something,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.63,0:12:32.93,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}he'll say something that gives me a hint...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.37,0:12:39.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's in this envelope?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.44,0:12:41.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, those are—
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.64,0:12:43.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,—from when I followed the guy—
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.71,0:12:45.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Uh oh! They're mixed up!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.18,0:12:48.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,—who got killed!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.45,0:12:51.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.59,0:12:54.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you alright, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.59,0:12:57.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did he give you a boo-boo?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.03,0:12:59.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Gimme a break.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.73,0:13:02.02,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Guess he is just a stupid kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.17,0:13:10.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Say, are you sure this is the guy who was killed?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.50,0:13:12.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,His body was all burned up...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.41,0:13:14.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it was definitely him.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.54,0:13:18.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,His driver's license was lying right next
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.28,0:13:22.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,to the flame tower at the fire festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.18,0:13:26.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The teeth even matched his dental records.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.95,0:13:28.09,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}That's strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.09,0:13:31.89,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Criminals normally hide their crimes;
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.89,0:13:35.23,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}it's far too intentional for the body\Nto be hidden under the fire
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.23,0:13:41.17,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}and an easily-understood clue to be lying nearby!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.17,0:13:44.30,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Only one person stood to gain from the body's discovery:
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.30,0:13:47.64,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Abe, who would get the insurance money.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.64,0:13:50.91,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}The old man's right—\Nhe's the only possible person!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.91,0:13:54.98,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}But he has an airtight alibi!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.98,0:14:00.25,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}No, there has to be something that will destroy his story!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.19,0:14:08.47,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}T-This is it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.10,0:14:14.19,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}This photograph!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.60,0:14:20.91,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}That's strange. The Negishi{\rHonorifics - Thoughts\be10}-san{\r\be10} I saw...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.91,0:14:23.71,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}...was right-handed!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.71,0:14:24.94,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Could it be?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.72,0:14:29.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.45,0:14:35.62,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Just as I thought!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.62,0:14:38.39,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}These are from Thursday and Friday.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.39,0:14:40.46,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}And these are from Saturday!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.50,0:14:44.00,Signs,,0,0,0,,Thursday
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.20,0:14:44.47,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}The old man followed Negishi{\rHonorifics - Thoughts\be10}-san{\r\be10}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.75,0:14:48.25,Signs,,0,0,0,,Friday
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.47,0:14:46.70,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}from Thursday to Saturday.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.00,0:14:52.75,Signs,,0,0,0,,Saturday
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.70,0:14:50.64,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}His body was found on Sunday night,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.25,0:14:55.72,Signs,,0,0,0,,Sunday
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.64,0:14:55.72,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}so the murder took place between Saturday night and Sunday evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.21,0:14:58.18,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}But Yutaka Abe was in Kyushu
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.18,0:15:03.05,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}from Saturday morning until Monday afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.05,0:15:05.49,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}His alibi is flawless!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.49,0:15:09.48,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}But if my theory is correct, then it's actually—
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.23,0:15:15.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mind your own business, twerp!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.83,0:15:18.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Look away for a second and he causes trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.83,0:15:23.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't hit Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} just because you can't solve the case!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.60,0:15:26.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yutaka Abe is clearly responsible for this!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.11,0:15:28.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He even has a motive!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.04,0:15:29.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Motive?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.71,0:15:33.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,His business was 300 million yen in debt.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.28,0:15:37.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He used the insurance money to pay it off
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.79,0:15:42.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and plans to escape overseas with the rest of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.39,0:15:43.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Overseas?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.72,0:15:47.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He left someone in charge of the company, saying that he was going on a trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.90,0:15:52.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And his plane leaves at 9:00 tonight!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.23,0:15:56.27,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}9:00?! That leaves us only three hours!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.27,0:15:58.91,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}We can't let him leave the country!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.91,0:16:03.68,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}My only chance now is to corner him\Nand make him confess!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.68,0:16:08.42,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}There's no time! First, I need to get them to the airport!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.42,0:16:11.75,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Alright! I'll use that method!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.75,0:16:17.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Eh? You destroyed Abe's alibi, Inspector?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.42,0:16:20.93,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Yes. I'm on my way to the airport.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.93,0:16:24.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'd like you to come too!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.77,0:16:27.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Excellent! I'll see you there!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.60,0:16:33.23,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Alright, now to use the old man's voice...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.18,0:16:41.75,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Hello, Inspector Megure! This is Kogoro Mouri!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.75,0:16:44.54,Character Card,,0,0,0,,New Tokyo International Airport
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.92,0:16:48.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Listen! Don't get in my way!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.32,0:16:49.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We won't!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.52,0:16:53.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You come every single time!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.73,0:16:55.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It sure is crowded.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.86,0:16:59.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just finding the Inspector is going to be tough...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.00,0:17:01.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Which flight is Abe's?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.70,0:17:03.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I think it was—
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.67,0:17:07.67,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Oh no! They're about to start boarding!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.67,0:17:14.45,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}It's dangerous, but I'll have to lure him out!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.45,0:17:20.99,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Paging Yutaka Abe{\rHonorifics - Radio\be10}-sama{\r\be10}, bound for Seattle
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.99,0:17:23.22,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}on Flight Number 99...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.22,0:17:28.50,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}...Masaki Negishi{\rHonorifics - Radio\be10}-sama{\r\be10} is waiting for you in the main parking lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.50,0:17:33.03,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Again, Yutaka Abe{\rHonorifics - Radio\be10}-sama{\r\be10}, bound for Seattle
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.03,0:17:35.54,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}on Flight Number 99—
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.54,0:17:38.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's going on, Dad?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.24,0:17:40.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.71,0:17:42.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Inspector Megure!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.65,0:17:44.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry I'm late!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.51,0:17:50.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Never mind that! How did you destroy Abe's alibi?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.72,0:17:54.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You said you found out how.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.72,0:17:56.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh? Where did Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} go?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.26,0:18:04.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That was clever of you, Mister.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.78,0:18:06.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who's there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.27,0:18:11.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Negishi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} actually died Friday night, didn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.14,0:18:15.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right. The day before you left on your trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.64,0:18:21.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then you had Detective Mouri follow a fake Negishi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} around the following day...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.25,0:18:23.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.08,0:18:26.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,...to make us think he was alive until Saturday.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.92,0:18:31.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You checked the date of the festival in advance, and just as you planned,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.53,0:18:34.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,his body was found on Sunday night.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.53,0:18:38.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,With his precise time of death indeterminable,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.33,0:18:40.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Detective Mouri's statement put it
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.93,0:18:44.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,between Saturday night and Sunday evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.94,0:18:46.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Damn you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.24,0:18:50.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then you returned Monday afternoon, as if nothing had happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.88,0:18:52.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thus, your alibi was created.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.62,0:18:55.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well? Am I right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.97,0:18:58.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A kid?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.25,0:19:02.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I heard the policemen talking about the case
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.16,0:19:06.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and I tried applying my own kind of logic!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.13,0:19:10.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Your mistake was the substitute you chose for Negishi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.06,0:19:12.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You might've fooled the detective,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.67,0:19:15.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but there's no fooling the camera!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.10,0:19:19.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Your actor was left-handed, unlike Negishi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.51,0:19:23.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Give yourself up. This place is crawling with police.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.42,0:19:33.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well done, my boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.75,0:19:39.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I, Yutaka Abe, was indeed Negishi Masaki's killer.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.33,0:19:44.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But I won't be turning myself in. I'm going to live it up overseas!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.16,0:19:49.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Eh? But I'll tell everyone that you confessed.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.84,0:19:54.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nobody'll believe you, kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.27,0:19:59.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But they might believe you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.58,0:20:03.85,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I, Yutaka Abe, was indeed Negishi Masaki's killer.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.55,0:20:07.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You little brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.05,0:20:09.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You have no idea what it's like
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.16,0:20:13.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,to have your business\Non the verge of bankruptcy!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.53,0:20:18.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He got what he deserved!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.07,0:20:24.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He was stupid enough to take out\Nsuch a huge insurance policy!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.07,0:20:26.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He had no idea I'd kill him!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.22,0:20:41.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And you were stupid enough\Nto let me kill you, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.25,0:20:44.36,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}You're the stupid one!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.36,0:20:47.49,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I was gonna let you off easy if you turned yourself in!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.49,0:20:49.26,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}But now you've gone too far!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.37,0:20:56.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll smash in that rotten head of yours!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.82,0:21:18.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What the heck?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.13,0:21:23.72,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I, Yutaka Abe, was indeed Masaki Negishi's killer.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.90,0:21:27.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who on earth did this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.39,0:23:05.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Geez!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.28,0:23:10.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's one lousy bastard to use me like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.35,0:23:14.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm glad they found the fake Negishi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} too!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.29,0:23:17.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Apparently Abe asked him\Nto wander around all day
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.46,0:23:20.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,for no specific reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.30,0:23:25.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What bothers me is what Abe said afterwards...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.87,0:23:29.97,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}It was the kid! He did this!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.97,0:23:32.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The only kid around then was—
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.78,0:23:39.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah, right!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.65,0:23:43.05,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}It ain't easy being a kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.16,0:23:53.66,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}So, Ran's all by herself?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.66,0:23:55.15,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Water?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.51,0:24:04.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ran!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.54,0:24:08.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Looks like these might be random murders...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.65,0:24:14.66,Signs,,0,0,0,,Next Conan:
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.66,0:24:19.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Next... Next Conan's Hint: Power failure
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.70,0:24:21.46,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Next time, finally, a two-parter!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.46,0:24:23.56,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Ran{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}'s in danger!
